A band of a mighty few flocked to the nation’s capital to champion for the arts during the White House Correspondents Weekend. I was fortunate to join this 2024 cohort of thecreativecoalition to plead our case on the dire need for arts in our communities both large and especially small. In time we will see the fruits of our labor. I’m hoping for the best. :)

I firmly believe in the power of the arts to connect, empower, heal and educate. Blessed am I to do what I love; embolden am I to advocate to help preserve it. Let’s keep the arts alive! ✊🏾💪🏾

#artsadvocacy #dc #nationscapital #creativecoalition #actorslife #loveandlight

Seth Milchick for President
“MDE and Waffle Parties for All!”

thecreativecoalition 

#righttobeararts #artsadvocacy #artsadvocacyday

Excited I am to join this group of artists to champion for the arts and funding arts programming in our communities. What makes it sweeter is advocating in my birthplace and minutes from my hometown: the DMV! What an opportunity. Let’s gooooooo! 💪🏾✊🏾

See ya on the Hill. thecreativecoalition 

Happy Arts Advocacy Day! 

#creativecoalition #artsadvocacy #arts #capitolhill #whitehouse #dc #dmv

Every year “The Volunteer 40 Under 40 recognizes forty alumni under the age of 40 who have excelled personally and professionally since completing their degree at UT Knoxville.” This year I join a class of distinguished alums! Thank you utknoxville and tennalum for the honor. Hope to see you all soon in Knoxville! #govols🍊 #utk #utktheatre #gratitude #2024

In honor of my 5 year Sobriety Anniversary I decided to treat myself with a trip to Tiffany and Co. I was nervous. Never have I been to Tiffany’s nor have I bought luxury jewelry for myself, but I felt I deserved it. At the flagship store on 5th Ave the staff was incredibly kind and patient. A special Thank You to Norma and Fabio for the laughs, support and guidance. Also thank you to jcameronbarnett for the recommendation; a class act through and through. 

5 years ago I made this commitment to sobriety. How grateful I am for the bountiful harvest, blossoming community, and strength of mind, body and spirit!

#sobriety #onedayatatime #year5 #gratitude #loveandlight #blackboyjoy #soberlife #tiffanyandco

I was in LA for less than 15 hours then back to Chicago to finish out an 8 show week at goodmantheatre with Good Night Oscar. So much for Work/Life Balance. It’s been a whirlwind but a ride I was grateful to take and guess what? The week is far from over. Thank you to all who made it possible! You are the real MVPs. Also, can we talk about how patriciaarquette and I are matching on the red carpet?!?! Totally unplanned. #severance #goodnightoscar #redeyeflight #chicago #la #actorslife

Today’s peaceful demonstration was beautiful, inspiring, and invigorating. I’m grateful for all the prayers and support from home and in the streets. Thank you to all who made it possible, brandonmurphyco and his amazing team. I echo the statement spoken today in unison: We are not to be feared, we are to be respected! #blacklivesmatter #blacktranslivesmatter #blackwomenlivesmatter #blackmenlivesmatter #blackqueerlivesmatter
